summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to City employment commonly referred to as the Fourth Quarter 2009 Employment Ordinance; establishing new titles and/or salaries; designating positions as exempt from Civil Service status; authorizing the Mayor to execute a memorandum of agreement between the City of Seattle and the International Federation of Professional and Technical Engineers, Local 17; providing no salary increase for Municipal Court Magistrates for 2010; and ratifying and confirming prior acts; all by a 2/3 vote of the City Council.
